ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋點解電腦要用2進制<br />\n我明以前係為咗易整 on/off 有電/冇電 表示0/1<br />\n但而家技術應該做到 用voltage大小 代表唔同數<br />\n<br />\n真心求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為電腦行2進制<br />\n同埋經驗話Digital signal (2進制) 比Analog signal (連續信號) 更好。因為用二進制，信息較不易受雜訊(noise)干擾，提高傳輸準確度。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"呢個理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解係8 唔係4/16/32"},{"pid":"0c8b46d16510eb8e501a1379f432b8436975ac3c","tid":814228,"uid":39531,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔係10bits 又易啲計<br />\n又點解唔係4/16/32<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋點解電腦要用2進制<br />\n我明以前係為咗易整 on/off 有電/冇電 表示0/1<br />\n但而家技術應該做到 用voltage大小 代表唔同數<br />\n<br />\n真心求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>因為電腦行2進制<br />\n同埋經驗話Digital signal (2進制) 比Analog signal (連續信號) 更好。因為用二進制，信息較不易受雜訊(noise)干擾，提高傳輸準確度。</blockquote>呢個理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解係8 唔係4/16/32</blockquote><br />\n見人地解釋係<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>如果要代表晒26個英文字母大小寫+符號及保留字,起碼要有200個字.<br />\n所以2^8=256,夠晒ASCII用.<br />\n所以一個byte有8個bit.<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7ad2689c330ff1c147bde535439aeb64da480b8a","tid":814228,"uid":208823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"方便計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1198656644215aaccd9a0a7426bbedaadb9c8c","tid":814228,"uid":139150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"The term &ldquo;byte&rdquo; was coined in the 1950&rsquo;s to refer to the addressable blocks of memory in the IBM 7030 Stretch computer. The size of a byte was variable, specified in the instruction, and was spelled &ldquo;byte&rdquo; to avoid accidentally getting shortened to &ldquo;bit&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nOther early computers worked with 4-bit bytes, 6-bit bytes, 7-bit bytes, based on the side of the character set they used and the choice of the hardware designer.<br />\n<br />\nThe extremely popular IBM System/360 mainframe used an 8-bit byte, which helped increase the popularity of 8 bits. <br />\n<br />\nTL;DR: 因為IBM出名所以8bit = 1byte"},{"pid":"7be56b75d17ceb9cca98348d010bf85b5895d0e1","tid":814228,"uid":201671,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c8b46d16510eb8e501a1379f432b8436975ac3c","tid":814228,"uid":39531,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔係10bits 又易啲計<br />\n又點解唔係4/16/32<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋點解電腦要用2進制<br />\n我明以前係為咗易整 on/off 有電/冇電 表示0/1<br />\n但而家技術應該做到 用voltage大小 代表唔同數<br />\n<br />\n真心求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>因為電腦行2進制<br />\n同埋經驗話Digital signal (2進制) 比Analog signal (連續信號) 更好。因為用二進制，信息較不易受雜訊(noise)干擾，提高傳輸準確度。</blockquote>呢個理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解係8 唔係4/16/32</blockquote><br />\n見人地解釋係<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>如果要代表晒26個英文字母大小寫+符號及保留字,起碼要有200個字.<br />\n所以2^8=256,夠晒ASCII用.<br />\n所以一個byte有8個bit.<br />\n</blockquote>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"噢 原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj